quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  55,26,Kala ko woni e hoore mayri ko ko re'ata
  55,27,"heddoo Jaati Joomi maa Kin, Jom mawngu e teddungal. @Corrected"
  55,28,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,29,"Ɓen wonɓe ka kammuuli e ka leydi hino naamnoo Mo. Ñalnde woo, Himo e fiyaaku"
  55,30,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,31,"Aray nde Men faandii hasbude on, onon yo tedda ko'e en ɗiɗo"
  55,32,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,33,"Ko onon yo dental jinna e yimɓe ! Si on hattanii wuɗɗirgol ka seraaji kammuuli e ka leydi, haray wuɗɗee. On wuɗɗirtaa si wanaa e doole"
  55,34,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,35,"Hino wurtee e mon - [onon jinna e yimɓe] - ɗemngal yiite e curki [maa sila taayuɗo], on faabondirtaa"
  55,36,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,37,"Si wonii kammu ngun seekike, ngu wojjirii wa piindi hono pentiir boɗe"
  55,38,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,39,"Nden ñalnde, wanaa neɗɗo maa jinne woni ko lanmditetee fii junuubi mun"
  55,40,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton
  55,41,Bomɓe ɓen hino annditiree maandeeji maɓɓe ɗin. Ɓe nanngiroyee ka njubuuji-tin tinɗi- e ka koyɗe
  55,42,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin woni ko fennoton
  55,43,Ko ngee woni Jahannama nge bomɓe ɓen fennaynoo fii mun
  55,44,Hiɓe wanngoo hakkunde magge e fatayɗam hattuɗam wulde
  55,45,E ko honɗi e neemaaji Joomi mon ɗin yeddoton